Meet <b>Trel</b>, our citizen of the week!<br><br>Trel has been living in Metro Park at <a href='/home/?user=supertrel22'>29890-C Main Street</a> ever since April 28th, 2007, which has given him just enough time to decorate his pad with some real style. <br><br>His all white Chamber of Entertainment is ultra chic and a perfect place to bump some tunes. If you are going to bring over some music to play, it should be easy to remember what you need to bring. Trel is into Rap, Pop, and more Rap. There's nothing wrong with a guy who knows what he likes.<br><br>I guess a lot of high-energy music comes in handy when you're collecting trophies. Trel has awards from a wide range of activities including Sink Three, Homerun Derby, Surfari, and riding the Half Pipe. <br><br>It's amazing that Trel still finds time among all of these activities to feed all of his pets. All totaled, he has 6 dogs and 18 fish. If he buys any more pets, Trel's home may end up turning into the official Millsberry Zoo.<br><br>When you see Trel, shake his hand and congratulate him for being such an upstanding citizen.</div>
